    <div class="details_section">
      <h3 class="ff_title fc_2 maki-swimming"> What to Do</h3>
      <p> There's a ton to see and do in Rhode Island and the surrounding states, especially in the summer.  Stay local to enjoy the Newport Mansions, the Narragansett Beaches, and state capital of providence.  Or, take a trip out to Boston, Cape Cod, or New York City - all are within a few hours of driving.  </p>
      <p> <%= link_to 'learn more...', ri_path, class: "ff_read right"%>  </p>
